author: Russell Brand
description:
"Discover Dr. Josh’s turmeric “hack” and take the first step toward pain-free living today! https://goldenrevive.com/BRAND"

Today I’m responding to a critique from Sam Seder and The Majority Report—watching it in full and in good faith. I reflect on faith, fallibility, and the tendency for culture to weaponize people as symbols. I talk about being used by the media, how Christ has reshaped my values, and why we need to find compassion even for those we disagree with. This isn’t about outrage—it’s about exploring how we can be better.
